    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Overall credibility assessment accepted at Medium assurance level. Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels. The single below-level factor (Test conditions, achieved Gradation 2 vs. required Gradation 3) is acknowledged and bounded: the single-condition limitation does not materially expand prediction uncertainty for the constrained COU scope, and supplementary testing is planned. The E/uval metric is satisfied for all three QoIs, and the model ensemble demonstrates consistent behavior across two independent laboratories. The Medium model risk level is appropriately matched by the Medium assurance level.",
